<section id="proceso" class="section-padding reveal">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header" style="text-align: center;">
            <h2>Tu propiedad lista en 4 pasos</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="process-row">
            <div class="process-step">
                <div class="step-circle">
                    <span class="step-num">1</span>
                </div>
                <h3>Agendamos</h3>
                <p>Coordinamos la visita a la propiedad en el horario que mejor te quede.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="process-step">
                <div class="step-circle">
                    <span class="step-num">2</span>
                </div>
                <h3>Capturamos</h3>
                <p>Fotograf&iacute;a profesional de alta gama usando equipo de &uacute;ltima generaci&oacute;n.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="process-step">
                <div class="step-circle">
                    <span class="step-num">3</span>
                </div>
                <h3>Transformamos</h3>
                <p>Nuestra tecnolog&iacute;a de staging digital decora los espacios vac&iacute;os con estilo.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="process-step">
                <div class="step-circle">
                    <span class="step-num">4</span>
                </div>
                <h3>Recib&iacute;s</h3>
                <p>En menos de 48hs ten&eacute;s todo el material listo para publicar y vender.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .process-row {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
        gap: 24px;
        position: relative;
    }

    .process-step {
        text-align: center;
        position: relative;
        padding: 0 16px;
    }

    .process-step::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 25px;
        right: calc(50% + 32px);
        left: calc(-50% + 32px);
        height: 1px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(232, 194, 122, 0.2), transparent);
    }

    .process-step:first-child::before {
        display: none;
    }

    .process-step h3 {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
        font-weight: 700;
    }

    .process-step p {
        color: var(--text-dim);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
        max-width: 260px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .step-circle {
        width: 50px;
        height: 50px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: transparent;
        border: 2px solid var(--accent-color);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        margin: 0 auto 24px;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
    }

    .step-num {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--accent-color);
        font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .process-row {
            gap: 48px;
        }

        .process-step::before {
            display: none;
        }
    }
</style>
